    "In our subsequent work, we will continue to add unrecorded signs to our database and include instructions in our sign language tutorials to highlight these subtle differences between similar signs.",
    "Additionally, some deaf parents further suggest adding voice navigation features to the IACH pages and selflearning modules to increase interactivity for their hearing children.",
    "This feature would make the IACH more engaging and easier to use, especially for younger users or those less familiar with technology.",
    "In our next development phase, we plan to update and incorporate these navigation features.",
    "On the other hand, some users have expressed a desire for faster response times from the software."
